{"tid":2516208,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法迪將接受半月板摘除手術 生涯或受影響","createTime":"2021-05-04T13:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T13:29:06.000Z","uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52e5f40d6476bdc082c726089ed4d607fe7d37f3","tid":2516208,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:21:51.000Z","msg":"據西班牙《世界體育報》報導，巴塞天才小將安蘇&middot;法迪（Ansu Fati）決定接受左膝半月板摘除手術，以徹底解決自己的膝部傷病問題。<br />\n<br />\n  本週四，安蘇&middot;法迪將接受手術，主刀的將是葡萄牙國家隊的隊醫。<br />\n<br />\n  此前安蘇&middot;法迪已經接受了三次的膝部手術，但一直都沒解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n  現在，經過各方專家會診，決定對安蘇&middot;法迪實施膝部半月板摘除手術。安蘇&middot;法迪預計要再養傷6到8個星期，他將無法參加今夏的歐國盃。<br />\n<br />\n  不過《世界體育報》也指出，摘除膝部半月板，長期來說會對法迪的膝關節造成影響，而他的職業生涯也可能因此受到影響。"},{"pid":"d1f57a72207c798c13c3934fcb219a38ad70440e","tid":2516208,"uid":17522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"Why is 葡萄牙隊醫"},{"pid":"85ca7f7bfc0040477002515d66e35b6111095a64","tid":2516208,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1f57a72207c798c13c3934fcb219a38ad70440e","tid":2516208,"uid":17522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"Why is 葡萄牙隊醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"唔知 不過fati本身係前葡萄牙殖民地出世"},{"pid":"72d0f185bf67e8db376717c192b8f191c37c19f5","tid":2516208,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被人燈死左"},{"pid":"5de9980ab676ac0fb47209530a998950236b918f","tid":2516208,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"同雲達華治一樣，會成日傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}